		<div class="entry-content"><div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/06/20/today-in-small-business-google-my-business/" data-title="Today in Small Business: Google My Business" data-description="Will Google&#039;s new portal help small businesses? Is it time to stop paying attention to click-through rates? And why you should give your sales force a checkup.">
				<div class="ad sharetools-inline-article-ad"></div>
				<div id="MiddleLeft" class="ad middle-left-ad nocontent robots-nocontent"></div>
				</div><div class="inlineModule"><div class="entry"><h6 class="kicker"><a href="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/category/dashboard/">Dashboard</a></h6><p class="summary">A daily roundup of small-business developments.</p></div></div>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">Whatâs affecting me, my clients and other small-business owners today.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>The Economy</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ The St. Louis Fedâs Financial Stress Index fell to an <a href="//www.stlouisfed.org/newsroom/financial-stress-index/assets/pdf/STLFSI-PressRelease-6-19-2014.pdf">record low</a> for the second time in three weeks.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Sales</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A sales expert explains why itâs important to give <a href="//blog.vistage.com/sales/giving-sales-force-checkup/?">your sales force</a> a checkup.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Marketing</b></p>
