<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A survey suggests that retailers plan to increase spending on <a href="//www.internetretailer.com/2014/06/19/retailers-plan-boost-spending-e-mail-marketing#.">email marketing</a>.</p>
